name: MealPlanner
0:
”Alexa, open meal planner.”
”What are we making?”
”Lets plan a meal.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: meal planner
des: Ever wanted to keep track of what you are making this week? Now you can do that with voice commands. Meal Planner tracks meals along with what day you are planning to make them as well as whether they are planned for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
